  <para>
    Below are links to test results for the 
    <ulink url="http://pmd.sf.net/">PMD</ulink> tests for the
    CDK modules. PMD is a tool to check for common errors in the source
    code, as well as style problems. The goal of this exercise is
    to gain a cleaner and more maintainable code base.
  </para>
  
  <para>
    The results given below are generated with an Ant build file which
    can be found in CVS: <filename>pmd.xml</filename>. It uses these
    tests:
  </para>
  
